description.S:
This family-friendly and business-friendly property in the popular Fisherman’s Wharf is a comfortable spot to call home base in San Francisco. Enjoy convenient amenities such as a 24-hour fitness center and business center, free Wi-Fi, and a family arcade/game room. A bar lounge, coffee shop, and snack bar offer guests easy meals onsite or on the go. Convenient onsite parking is also available for an additional fee. For family fun or business travel in the heart of San Francisco, this property is an ideal choice.

PLEASE NOTE:
- The destination fee is not included in the daily rate. A mandatory destination fee of $37.34/night per accommodation will be collected upon arrival.
- The maximum number of days that you may book per reservation is only 28 days.
- The listing is distributed and managed by RoomPicks Accommodations.

THE SPACE

This 322sf Deluxe Two Queens features:
- 2 Queen beds;
- Daily housekeeping;
- Coffee maker;
- All linens, towels, and bathroom essentials are provided. You don’t need to bring a thing!!

THE PROPERTY

Our family-friendly property provides the following on-site amenities:
- 24/7 Front desk and Security;
- On-site coffee shop and bar;
- Fitness center;
- Business center;
- Snack bar;
- Game room;
- Pets up to 50 lbs are allowed and are limited to 1 pet per room for an extra charge of $100 per pet per stay;
- Private parking is available(parking slot reservation is not required in advance) and costs $62 per day + tax.

Unwind in one of our elegantly furnished rooms with flat-screen TVs, refrigerators, and free WIFI, among other amenities, after a long day. Enjoy fine dining at one of our on-site restaurants, where brilliant chefs create delectable delicacies. Visit our pubs and lounges to unwind and socialize while enjoying drinks and a distinctive atmosphere. We provide front desk assistance around-the-clock, and our exercise center is a fantastic location to stay in shape or burn some calories. By working efficiently in our business center and conference rooms to complete your projects and hold meetings, you won't ever have to worry about missing a deadline. Throughout your stay, indulge in modern amenities and first-rate service while feeling at ease and relaxed.

PLEASE NOTE:
- The listing is distributed and managed by RoomPicks Accommodations.
- Please note that the resort fee is not included in the daily rate. A mandatory resort fee of $33.77/night per unit will be collected upon arrival.

THE UNIT

This 247sf Grand King High Floor and View features:
- 1 King bed;
- Daily housekeeping;
- Coffee maker, Refrigerator;
- Inner courtyard view;
- 55-inch flat-screen TV;
- Air conditioning;
- Laptop workspace;
- Desk;
- Free bottled water;
- All linens, towels, and bathroom essentials are provided. You don’t need to bring a thing!!

THE PROPERTY

Our family-friendly property provides the following on-site amenities:
- 24/7 Front desk and Security;
- On-site restaurant and bar;
- Fitness center;
- Business center;
- Laundry facilities;
- Pet bowls;
- Bicycle rental (Additional charge);
- Free crib;
- Accessible by disabled guests;
- Daily cooked-to-order breakfast available 7:00 AM–11:00 AM for a fee: USD 15–45 for adults and USD 10–20 for children;
- Pets are allowed; for an extra charge of USD 87.33 per pet, per night. 2 per room (up to 50 lbs per pet).
- Private parking is available at a site (parking slot reservation is not required in advance) and costs USD 67 per day.
